insert into oglasi (id, naziv, kat_id, pos_id, url, opis_posla, rok_prijave) values (363, 'Senior Launch Manager (m/f)', 7, 398, 'https://www.moj-posao.net/Posao/487209/Senior-Launch-Manager-mf/', 'Xellia Pharmaceuticals is a leading developer, manufacturer and supplier of life-saving anti-infectives. With over 100 years of industry experience in developing last resort treatments for infectious diseases, Xellia is focused on the supply of products which not only save lives, but also improve and enhance patients’ quality of life. We are a specialty pharmaceutical company focused on fermented antibiotics and injectable finished products. Headquartered in Copenhagen, Denmark, and owned by Novo A/S, we are more than 1500 employees globally. From state-of-the-art manufacturing sites in the U.S, China, Denmark and Hungary to R&D sites in Norway and Croatia; Xellia Pharmaceuticals excels within innovative product development to deliver high quality products.  For our Zagreb team we are looking for Senior Launch Manager (m/f) Global Launch Office   Are you a launch manager with 5+ years of relevant experience and ideally knowledge of the anti-infective injectable generics business?  In this position, you will be part of Xellia Pharmaceuticals’ Global Launch Office, where you get to manage various number of launches of injectable anti-infective generics and innovative products, developed and manufactured by Xellia Pharmaceuticals or CMOs, into the global market (US, Asia, EU, ROW) either via B2B (business to business) and B2i (business to institution) commercial channels. Xellia Pharmaceuticals has ambitious growth plans and with that comes increasing number of launches, wherefore the Global Launch Office is expanding. The team is part of the R&D and Strategic Projects department, managed by the Director of Global Launch Office.Successful product launches require skillful management and coordination across numerous stakeholders. You will be responsible for launches which includes detailed planning and coordination with various key stakeholders both internally and externally, seeing through the actual launch and monitoring post launch performance while ensuring a thorough hand over to operations, ensuring business continuity, be it via the B2B or B2i commercial channel. Your key stakeholders will be placed in several locations around the world and in different functions:  Commercial, Marketing, Regulatory Affairs, R&D, Strategic Projects, Operations, Manufacturing, Quality, Planning, Business development, Portfolio etc. Main tasks: Ensuring successful launch execution from beginning of project to hand over to operations, of Xellia produced products or at CMOs
